  id: Space Junk Field
  displayName: Space Junk Field
  introText: Your sensors pick up a dangerous field of debris.  Navigating through
    it might let you harvest some valuable salvage, but is dangerous.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Navigate through
    outcomeText: Salvage is everywhere.  But the debris batters your ship.
